WEBVTT

00:02.768 --> 00:04.998
I commend thy soul
to God the Father Almighty...

00:05.037 --> 00:06.834
and thy body to the ground...

00:06.872 --> 00:10.968
earth to earth, ashes to ashes,
and dust to dust...

00:11.010 --> 00:13.171
Damn it. We're late already.
Is my tie on straight?

00:13.212 --> 00:14.338
Yeah.

00:14.380 --> 00:15.847
You really can't miss with a clip-on.

00:15.881 --> 00:17.007
We never should have stopped.

00:17.049 --> 00:18.346
Why is it every time
I need to get somewhere...

00:18.384 --> 00:20.818
We get waylaid by
jackassery? Pants!

00:20.853 --> 00:22.684
But it was a good thing we did, Pop.

00:22.721 --> 00:24.348
The ant people needed our help.

00:24.390 --> 00:25.516
Help, schmelp.

00:25.557 --> 00:27.024
The big reward they promised us...

00:27.059 --> 00:28.993
was nothing but
an old, licked-up Jolly Rancher.

00:29.028 --> 00:32.020
But they did give us the key
to their enchanted underground city.

00:32.064 --> 00:35.363
And Brock made special
friends with their queen.

00:35.401 --> 00:37.198
You can't put a price on that.

00:37.236 --> 00:39.033
My point exactly.

00:39.071 --> 00:41.301
You trying paying the electric bill with...

00:43.075 --> 00:45.043
Who shall change our vile body...

00:45.077 --> 00:47.136
that it may be like unto
his glorious, eternal super-body...

00:47.179 --> 00:48.373
Holy!

